<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٠٦ - وَأَخْبَرَنَا أَبُو بَكْرٍ الْمَرُّوذِيُّ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ وَذَكَرَ مَوْعِدًا،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِنْ قُدِّرَ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>